    <footnotes>
        <footnote id="F1">The Phantom Units were awarded to the reporting person by CVR Partners, LP on December 29, 2017, as compensation for services as an officer. These Incentive Units vest ratably in three annual installments beginning in December of each year following the grant date, subject to the terms of the award agreement.</footnote>
